      "problem_latex": "Which set of numbers go into the missing blanks respectively to make the equation true?  $7=14$ $\\div$~\\uline{~~~~~~~~~~}~$=\\frac{14}{\\square}=\\frac{14}{1}\\times\\frac{1}{\\square}$\n(A) 2, 1, 2\n(B) 1, 2, 2\n(C) 2, 2, 1\n(D) 2, 2, 2",
