    "content": {
      "language": "en",
      "problem_latex": "After simplying the following expressions, which one is different from others?\n(A) (x+y)-(x-y)\n(B) (2x+3y)+(-2x-y)\n(C) (3x-2y)+(-3x+4y)\n(D) (x-y)+(-x+y)",
      "problem_plain": "After simplying the following expressions, which one is different from others? (A) (x+y)-(x-y) (B) (2x+3y)+(-2x-y) (C) (3x-2y)+(-3x+4y) (D) (x-y)+(-x+y)",
      "solution_latex": "$(x+y)-(x-y)=2y$  $(2x+3y)+(-2x-y)=2x+3y-2x-y=2y$  $(3x-2y)+(-3x+4y)=3x-2y-3x+4y=2y$  $(x-y)+(-x+y)=x-y-x+y=0$",
      "solution_plain": "(x+y)-(x-y)=2y (2x+3y)+(-2x-y)=2x+3y-2x-y=2y (3x-2y)+(-3x+4y)=3x-2y-3x+4y=2y (x-y)+(-x+y)=x-y-x+y=0"
    },
